    "rationale": "The credibility assessment for COU1 is accepted. Seven of thirteen factors were formally assessed; all assessed factors met or exceeded their required gradation levels at MRL 2. Six factors were appropriately scoped out or not assessed per the MRL 2 requirements matrix. The CFD model is deemed sufficiently credible to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
